          Show up. <span style="color:#22C55E">Call the number.</span> Close the deal.
        </h2>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.85rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          <div id="ss1" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(18px);display:flex;gap:.85rem;align-items:flex-start;padding:.9rem 1rem;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07)">
            <div style="width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(34,197,94,.12);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,.3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:.8rem;flex-shrink:0">🚶</div>
            <div><div style="font-weight:700;font-size:.88rem;margin-bottom:.2rem">Show up at their door</div><div style="font-size:.78rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.38);line-height:1.55">Target contractors with vans or storefronts. Plumbers, HVAC, roofers — San Diego.</div></div>
          </div>
          <div id="ss2" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(18px);display:flex;gap:.85rem;align-items:flex-start;padding:.9rem 1rem;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07)">
            <div style="width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(34,197,94,.12);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,.3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:.8rem;flex-shrink:0">📞</div>
            <div><div style="font-weight:700;font-size:.88rem;margin-bottom:.2rem">Call the number in front of them</div><div style="font-size:.78rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.38);line-height:1.55">They hear the AI answer their own line. Demo sells itself. No pitch deck needed.</div></div>
          </div>
          <div id="ss3" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(18px);display:flex;gap:.85rem;align-items:flex-start;padding:.9rem 1rem;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(34,197,94,.06);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,.3)">
            <div style="width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(34,197,94,.2);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,.5);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:.8rem;flex-shrink:0">✅</div>
            <div><div style="font-weight:700;font-size:.88rem;margin-bottom:.2rem;color:#22C55E">They sign up on the spot</div><div style="font-size:.78rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.38);line-height:1.55">14-day free trial. No contract. Card on file. Live in 20 minutes.</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:.82rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.28);font-style:italic">"The product demos itself. That's the whole play."</div>
